01:53:31.805 --> 01:53:33.014
No, no!

01:53:35.934 --> 01:53:39.187
I only discovered it
by chance when I started
representing myself

01:53:39.271 --> 01:53:40.813
six years
into my sentence!

01:53:40.898 --> 01:53:42.482
But there it was
in the court file.

01:53:42.566 --> 01:53:45.026
