Counselor,

01:54:54.179 --> 01:54:56.556
guilty of betraying
your fellow man,

01:54:56.640 --> 01:54:58.558
guilty of
betraying your country,

01:54:58.642 --> 01:55:00.601
guilty of
abrogating your oath,

01:55:00.686 --> 01:55:03.563
