and to die like one.

01:56:03.206 --> 01:56:04.874
Give me your hand!

01:56:18.722 --> 01:56:20.056
(EXCLAIMING)

01:56:38.283 --> 01:56:39.825
No!

01:56:39.910 --> 01:56:41.410
Go! Go!

01:56:42.496 --> 01:56:43.704
(BOTH SCREAMING)

01:56:49.044 --> 01:56:50.836
